[0.025, "o", "\r\nThe files in the `/Users/roberto/mcp-bridge/examples/demo/sample-files` directory are:\r\n\r\n* `README.md`: a Markdown file containing information about the sample files\r\n* `notes.txt`: a text file containing notes or comments\r\n* `todo.txt`: a text file containing to-do items or tasks\r\n\r\nThese files appear to be example files used for demonstration purposes, possibly related to the MCP-bridge project.\r\n"]
